          <div class="pp-why-row"><span class="pp-why-check">✓</span>Twisted loop weave</div>
          <div class="pp-why-row"><span class="pp-why-check">✓</span>Zero swirl marks</div>
          <div class="pp-why-row"><span class="pp-why-check">✓</span>300+ machine washes</div>
          <div class="pp-why-row"><span class="pp-why-check">✓</span>Safe on PPF and ceramic</div>
